data.description: Investment Opportunity in San Antonio, Texas!    Welcome to 344 Belmont, a fixer-upper gem with incredible income potential minutes away from Downtown San Antonio! This property boasts 2 spacious bedrooms and 2 expansive living areas, providing a solid foundation for a lucrative investment. With room to expand, this is your chance to maximize returns by adding value to the property. Don't miss out on this opportunity in the heart of San Antonio!
